Using APT (Recommended for Simplicity)
Open Terminal: Press Ctrl+Alt+T.
Update Package List:
bash
sudo apt update
Install VirtualBox:
bash
sudo apt install virtualbox virtualbox-ext-pack
This installs VirtualBox and the Extension Pack, adding USB support and other features.
Install Guest Additions (for inside the VM):
bash
sudo apt install virtualbox-guest-utils virtualbox-guest-x11
